nodes.text: Delpho was a Human male who served as a soldier with the Galactic Alliance Guard. He was a member of Major Salle Serpa's battalion, which occupied the Jedi Academy on Ossus during the Second Galactic Civil War. In the ensuing Battle of Ossus, Delpho was responsible for pumping coma gas into Jaina Solo's room; however, she was able to overpower him and knock him unconscious.
